1
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:43,399
Are you waiting for her?

2
00:00:45,399 --> 00:00:46,200
Jiao Jing.

3
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:46,960
Zhu Yihai.

4
00:00:47,759 --> 00:00:49,479
You fell for it after all.

5
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,079
It's over.

6
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,759
We left Director Ge behind.

7
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:56,079
Who is it? I'm busy!

8
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,319
Enough.

9
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:20,519
Ge Zhendong is already on his way.

10
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:23,920
You're useless now.

11
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,879
Keep an eye on him.

12
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:38,840
What are you doing here?

13
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,200
Sun Qian.

14
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,680
Don't just stand there. Tie them up!

15
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,560
Do you even know how?

16
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,640
Tie the two of them together.

17
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,560
Got it?

18
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:02,400
Hurry up!

19
00:02:03,159 --> 00:02:04,280
Listen up.

20
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,560
This is a huge deal.

21
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,879
None of you better drop the ball.

22
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:18,479
Secretary Yu, it'll be done soon.

23
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,199
Within the hour,

24
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,479
Aimin Street will be yours.

25
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,599
Come on, now.

26
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:28,000
This Ledger is Long Xiao's lifeline.

27
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,879
Of course I'd keep it on me.

28
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,000
Good.

29
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,800
Boss Long.

30
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:35,560
What is it?

31
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,039
Zhu Yihai's got someone in the club.

32
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,479
I caught her.

33
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,520
Fine, got it.

34
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:47,000
Boss Long, shouldn't you go question her?

35
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:49,680
Step outside for now.

36
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:53,680
Boss Long.

37
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,479
One moment.

38
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,319
I've got something here

39
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,199
to take care of.

40
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,919
Are you lecturing me?

41
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,719
Boss Long.

42
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:02,639
Director Ge is here.

43
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:12,599
Everyone, get out here!

44
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,719
Brother Hai, Brother Hai.

45
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,439
I've got a knife on me.

46
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,639
Take it.

47
00:03:26,879 --> 00:03:28,080
All of you, line up out here!

48
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:28,759
Move it!

49
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,479
What kind of game

50
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,360
is he playing now?

51
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,680
Boss Long.

52
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:39,439
Zhu Yihai's lackey, Xiong Dali.

53
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,000
I know him.

54
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:43,560
Security Chief, Dao Balian.

55
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,000
I know him well.

56
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,520
They got in my way of dealing with Ge Zhendong.

57
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,080
So I'll deal with them.

58
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,759
Brought them here today

59
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,319
for you to handle, Boss Long.

60
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,759
So, Ge Zhendong.

61
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:06,680
Excellent.

62
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,080
Wonderful.

63
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,680
Jiao Jing, you bitch!

64
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,279
Lied to Brother Hai again!

65
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:23,639
Let me go, I'll kill you!

66
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:26,079
Xiong Dali, oh Xiong Dali.

67
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,319
How is it that even now,

68
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:30,480
you haven't learned a damn thing?

69
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,680
You stay put.

70
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:39,879
Find somewhere safe.

71
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:48,279
So Long Xiao really is making a run for it.

72
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,240
Boss Long.

73
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:54,240
I was just doing my job.

74
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,600
Please, spare me.

75
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,959
Just let me go, yeah?

76
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:02,160
Xiong Dali, look, what a great attitude.

77
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,160
Right?

78
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,319
Learn a thing or two from him.

79
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,399
Director Ge.

80
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:18,240
Bringing you in like this,

81
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,959
you don't mind, do you?

82
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,399
I, Long Xiao,

83
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,959
am a businessman too.

84
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,959
I don't want to get rough unless I have to.

85
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:31,399
But please don't push me.

86
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:32,560
Alright?

87
00:05:34,519 --> 00:05:37,800
Let's sign this agreement today.

88
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:46,319
How about it?

89
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,680
Where's the agreement?

90
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:11,240
Long Xiao is desperate to get out of here now

91
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,279
because his bosses only gave him two days

92
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,360
to handle the Aimin Street situation.

93
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,199
I don't think we can just sit and wait to die.

94
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:18,120
But Long Xiao has too many men.

95
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:21,160
Zhu Yihai, do you have a plan?

96
00:06:21,759 --> 00:06:24,560
To take down Long Xiao and his backers together,

97
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,639
we have to find proof of their collusion.

98
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:58,759
Here.

99
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,079
Director Ge.

100
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:02,360
I've got the agreement ready.

101
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,920
Let's settle this today.

102
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,720
Come on.

103
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,360
Xie Fan.

104
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:16,519
What kind of game are you playing?

105
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:19,360
Long Xiao, where've you hidden Huilian?

106
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,680
Long Xiao.

107
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,839
Didn't see this coming, huh?

108
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,800
Even you can get outsmarted one day.

109
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:30,079
Boss Long.

110
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,360
Surprised, aren't you?

111
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:36,360
I told Long Xiao where you were hiding,

112
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,600
so you could prepare in advance

113
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,079
and wipe out most of his men.

114
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:41,279
Jiao Jing.

115
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,360
Let's do it this way.

116
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,639
Who are you?

117
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,319
I'm here for the agreement.

118
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,879
What agreement?

119
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:49,639
Who are you?

120
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:50,879
Xie Fan.

121
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,399
Long time no see.

122
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,199
Li Erhu.

123
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,360
Oh, that's right.

124
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:55,680
Little Fan.

125
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:58,399
You really messed up Dongxing Factory back then.

126
00:07:58,399 --> 00:08:00,120
Now you're in my hands.

127
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:08,439
You? A hitman? At your level?

128
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:09,240
Exactly.

129
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:12,160
Lili, come take a picture.

130
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:13,759
Lili.

131
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:16,279
This is Dao Balian's first time catching a bad guy.

132
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,920
A once in a lifetime moment.

133
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:18,879
Come on, come on.

134
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,360
One more.

135
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,319
All your dirty deals and plans with Secretary Yu,

136
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,800
I know everything.

137
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,759
In your plans,

138
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:30,720
I was never part of them, was I?

139
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,519
Zhu Yihai.

140
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:37,000
Zhu Yihai.

141
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:41,080
You actually betrayed me for Zhu Yihai?

142
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,960
Without me,

143
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:46,279
you'd still be a bar hostess.

144
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,799
Yes.

145
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,600
You pulled me out of one abyss,

146
00:08:57,519 --> 00:09:00,159
but dragged me into another.

147
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:02,480
For six years,

148
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,120
for your so-called business,

149
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:09,600
how many unspeakable things have I done?

150
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,879
I hoped you could trust me,

151
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,159
treat me like family.

152
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,600
But you didn't.

153
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,799
Secretary Yu.

154
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:23,679
It's falling apart.

155
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,320
Liu Tianqi's been caught.

156
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,840
They'll trace it back to me soon.

157
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,080
What do you mean?

158
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,600
I'm pulling out.

159
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,360
You've made this big a mess,

160
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,080
and you think you can just walk away?

161
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,559
Of course, I don't have to leave.

162
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,240
Worst case, I do time.

163
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:43,440
But our Ledger from all these years,

164
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,320
aren't you worried about that?

165
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:49,600
I'll say it again.

166
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:51,000
Aimin Street is the future

167
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,600
entertainment hub of all Night City.

168
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,720
I know, I promise I'll get it.

169
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,720
What guarantee can you give?

170
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:09,879
Secretary Yu.

171
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,799
She's Zhu Yihai's woman.

172
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:12,799
With her in hand,

173
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:15,480
I guarantee I'll take Aimin Street.

174
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,440
Wrap things up within two days,

175
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,720
and I'll get you out of Night City.

176
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,200
Don't worry.

177
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,480
I won't leave any loose ends.

178
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,759
Everyone involved,

179
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:29,279
I'll take care of every last one.

180
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,080
Come in.

181
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,759
Oh, you came just in time.

182
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,799
Help me pack my bags, quick.

183
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,919
I have to leave town.

184
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,399
Mm.

185
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,960
Then let me go with you.

186
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:48,960
Oh, come on.

187
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,080
It's just a business trip.

188
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:50,840
I'll be back soon.

189
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,120
Huh?

190
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,840
Really?

191
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,240
Really.

192
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:57,639
I'll be back in a couple of days.

193
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,799
So in the end, you don't want to take me.

194
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,519
Why?

195
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,799
Why won't you?

196
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,960
If you really think

197
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:10,000
all of this is some kind of favor,

198
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,639
then let me tell you this.

199
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:17,360
Every single second I've spent with you,

200
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:19,840
I've wished you were dead.

201
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,000
Shut up!

202
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,559
I'll kill you!

203
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:23,519
Jiao Jing!
